Portilla, drove them from the mountains, near the sea, turning their formidable trenches.

abstract: HARRISBURG, Penn., Nov. 11. Rufus Shipley, of Philadelphia, to-day made an application before the Governor and Board of Pardons for the appointment of a commission of experts to inquire into the sanity of Heidenblut, who murdered the German bakar in Philadelphia. abstract: WASHINGTON, NOV. 16--1 A. M.--Generally clear weather prevails in New-England, the Middle States, the lake region, and the Northwest, with variable winds and higher temperature east of Lake Michigan. The Mississippi River has risen at Cairo.

abstract: A reward of $10,000 has been, with commendable promptitude, offered by the municipality of Seville for the recovery of the celebrated picture by  Murillo, the "St. Anthony," which has so long  adorned the Capella de la Pila, in the Cathedral of the Andalusian capital, and which was recently spirited away by some clever thief.
